CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773057801
OL,3,CUK marks national Covid-19 day of
OL,4,Creflection six years on from pandemic
OL,6,FBereaved families have vowed to keep
OL,7,Ffighting for justice in memory of
OL,8,Ftheir loved ones as the final witness
OL,9,Ftestimony was heard, and there are
OL,10,Fseveral more inquiry reports due to be
OL,11,Fpublished this year and next.
OL,13,FAt least 248,000 people in the UK have
OL,14,Fdied with Covid-19 listed as a cause
OL,15,Fof death, according to the latest
OL,16,Favailable data published by the UK's
OL,17,Fstatistics agencies.
OL,19,FSunday's events are expected to
OL,20,Finclude gatherings and commemorations
OL,21,Facross the four nations of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
