CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773057801
OL,3,CUK marks national Covid-19 day of
OL,4,Creflection six years on from pandemic
OL,6,FAmong them will be a short ceremony at
OL,7,Fthe National Covid Memorial Wall in
OL,8,FLondon where a wreath will be placed
OL,9,Fand a minute's silence held at midday.
OL,11,FIn Wales, Caerphilly County Borough
OL,12,FCouncil will host people at the Ynys
OL,13,FHywel Covid Memorial Woodland, with an
OL,14,Finformal guided walk and a minute's
OL,15,Fsilence, while in Northern Ireland
OL,16,Flive music, poetry and reflective
OL,17,Fspeeches will take place at Belfast
OL,18,FCity Hall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
