CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773057801
OL,3,CUK marks national Covid-19 day of
OL,4,Creflection six years on from pandemic
OL,6,FCommunity and faith leaders,
OL,7,Fhealthcare professionals and local
OL,8,Fpeople will gather in Manchester for a
OL,9,Fmemorial service, storytelling and
OL,10,Freflection organised by the Caribbean
OL,11,Fand African Health Network (CAHN).
OL,13,FOn Saturday in Scotland, a gathering
OL,14,Fwas held at the Sails Sculpture in
OL,15,FGlasgow Green where there was also a
OL,16,Fminute's silence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
