OL,3,CUK marks national Covid-19 day of
OL,4,Creflection six years on from pandemic
OL,6,FCulture minister Baroness Twycross
OL,7,Fsaid: "Whenever I walk along the
OL,8,FNational Covid Memorial Wall, I'm
OL,9,Fstruck by the 250,000 hand-painted
OL,10,Fhearts that stretch for half a
OL,11,Fkilometre. It is a powerful tribute to
OL,12,Floved ones who will not be forgotten.
OL,14,F"The pandemic impacted everyone, up
OL,15,Fand down the country. It touched us
OL,16,Fall, and the impact of Covid remains.
OL,17,FWe now have the opportunity to come
OL,18,Ftogether as a nation to remember the
OL,19,Fquarter of a million lives lost.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
