PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773057801
OL,3,CUK marks national Covid-19 day of
OL,4,Creflection six years on from pandemic
OL,6,F"We also pay tribute to those on the
OL,7,Ffront line during the pandemic, who
OL,8,Fmade enormous sacrifices, day in, day
OL,9,Fout, to keep the British public safe `
OL,10,Fwhether in health and social care,
OL,11,Feducation, policing, transport or
OL,12,Fother frontline services.
OL,14,F"I encourage everyone to mark this day
OL,15,Fin a way that feels right for them,
OL,16,Fwhether attending a community event or
OL,17,Ftaking a quiet moment of reflection at
OL,18,Fhome."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
